          @Decimal.Round((Model.ProductsWithoutImage / ((decimal)Model.TotalProducts / 100)), 1)
          %</span>
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>
        <span class="portlet-content-column"><a href="#" onclick="Concentrator.ViewInstance.open('content-item',{MediaAndSpecs : false})">
          Products without any media or specifications :</a></span>
      </td>
